title: The Demonic Cult Leader Is Too Reluctant
description: The Demonic Cult Leader Is Too Reluctant Manhwa 전전긍긍 마교교주, The Reluctant Demonic Cult Leader, The Anxious Demon Cult Leader “Crazy bastards, just leave me be.” The story of Do Yugang, son of the Heavenly Demon, who dreads becoming the Demonic Cult Leader.
